<div class="recipe row">
  <div class="title col-md-12">
    <h2 id="everyday-pickles">
      Everyday Pickles</h2>
  </div>

  <div class="instructions col-md-6">
    <h3>Ingredients</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>1 garden fresh cucumber</li>
      <li>Salt</li>
      <li>Pepper</li>
      <li>Apple cider vinegar</li>
    </ul>

    <h4>Directions</h4>
    <p>Peel cucumber lengthwise leaving some small strips of peel. Slice into ¼ inch slices and add salt and cover with water. Let soak for 5-10 minutes. Drain. Cover in apple cider vinegar and serve.</p>
  </div>
</div>

