  </div>

  <div class="instructions col-md-6">
    <h3>Ingredients</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>8 cucumbers</li>
      <li>2 cup sugar and 2 cup apple cider vinegar and ¼ cup salt - mix until syrupy</li>
      <li>1 onion</li>
    </ul>

    <h4>Directions</h4>
    <p>Slice cukes and onion, In each quart add: ⅔ t tumeric, celery seed, mustard seed</p>
    <p>Store in fridge</p>
  </div>
